cx.corp.lacuna.core.windows.winapi

Interface Kernel32

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.sun.jna.AltCallingConvention, CloseHandle, GetProcessId, com.sun.jna.Library, OpenProcess, QueryFullProcessImageName, ReadProcessMemory, com.sun.jna.win32.StdCall, com.sun.jna.win32.StdCallLibrary

    public interface Kernel32
extends CloseHandle, OpenProcess, QueryFullProcessImageName, GetProcessId, ReadProcessMemory
    Proxy interface to the Windows API kernel32.dll library.

    In order to map the Java-style camelCase method names to the correct PascalCase names, CamelToPascalCaseFunctionMapper can be used.

    See Also:
    WinApiBootstrapper
    This is a Windows API interface used to proxy API calls via JNA. This interface is not meant to be used directly.
